# Week 2: UML Diagrams and System Design

## Objectives
- Model the chatbot system using UML diagrams.
- Define system architecture and component interactions.

## Activities Completed
- Created the following diagrams:
  - Use Case Diagram
  - Activity Diagram
  - Sequence Diagram
  - Class Diagram
  - Component Diagram
  - Deployment Diagram
  - State Diagram
  - Data Flow Diagram

## Deliverables
- `.png` images of each diagram
- Diagram descriptions

## Key Design Notes
- Modular architecture using React and Gemini API
- Stateless backend with structured document querying
- Clear separation of frontend, backend, and data layers

## Next Steps
- Conduct literature survey to compare existing chatbot solutions.
